Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:02.45,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,The Literature Club is a female-dominated society.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.45,0:00:04.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I'm the only male first-year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:08.29,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,They say that when three people gather, factions can form.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.29,0:00:09.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,In the case of the Literature Club,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:12.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I feel like it's divided between me and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:20.49,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Hey, Nukumizu-kun, hurry up and come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:23.41,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,What's wrong? If you're tired, I can give you a piggyback ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:25.36,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,D-don't dawdle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:27.71,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,I-if you let your guard down, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:34.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Today, I'm here at Nonhoi Park with the four first-year members of the Literature Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:37.68,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,We came to take photos for the website, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:40.65,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,...there's a reason we all came here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:43.20,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,The number of views.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:44.84,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Numbers can be cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:49.52,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,If a hierarchy forms among the three of them, cracks in their friendship will form!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:51.67,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,For now, I'm just winging it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:55.24,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,...the day when they learn the truth isn't too far off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:01:00.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,That's why I'll upload a picture of the three of them together on the website, and fool them a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.98,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Hey, Nukumizu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:08.55,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Happy-chan the sun bear was so cute, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.55,0:01:11.44,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Even though she's all alone as a girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:14.23,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,She's so lively and admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.11,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,You really feel a sense of sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.11,0:01:19.23,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, I heard a male sun bear arrived recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:22.70,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It wasn't out today, but it seems like they're getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:23.24,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:25.98,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:29.85,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Happy-chan has a boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:34.36,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,I thought she was like me, but I've been betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:37.65,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Yanami, you're getting kind of weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:39.45,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It's best to just leave this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.40,0:01:41.45,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Um,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:43.62,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Yakishio, which animal did you like best?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:44.98,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:48.35,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,I liked the African dormice at the nocturnal animal exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:50.16,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Oh, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.77,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Dormice are cute, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.77,0:01:55.15,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Those little guys scurry around in the dark, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.15,0:01:58.12,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,When you watch them, your eyes gradually get used to it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:01.27,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,You stop wanting to fight them because of how cute they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:03.35,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Animals aren't our enemies, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:07.69,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Speaking of the nocturnal animal exhibit, the aardvark was cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:11.49,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,Y-you like aardvarks too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:15.08,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,After watching that nose twitch for about five minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:19.18,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It kind of makes you forget everyday struggles and feel relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:22.06,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,I-I could watch them for 10 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:23.98,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,W-watch it jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:26.23,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Seriously? Aardvarks are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:31.20,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Today, we're going the usual route at Nonhoi Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:33.48,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,We're focusing on the zoo area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:36.28,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,When I'm with the Literature Club members,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:37.85,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,trouble is to be expected, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.91,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,...today is going surprisingly smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:40.84,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:43.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,If I had to take a guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:46.53,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, Yanami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:48.75,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,You haven't eaten anything today, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.46,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Is there some health problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:52.28,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Why would you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:55.54,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,I'm so healthy that even the doctor has given up on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:57.64,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean it's too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.76,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,But if Yanami hasn't eaten anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:02.74,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I'm starting to feel a bit uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.65,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,What is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:07.28,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Are you really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:10.20,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,There are a lot of food trucks out on the main street.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:10.84,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:11.89,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,The main street...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:15.35,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,I think I'm good for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:17.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,What's up, Yanami-sa—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.34,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Stop, Nukkun. Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:21.62,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Hey, don't pull me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:23.48,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.98,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,When we came here for the fake boyfriend thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.98,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Over there by the canal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Hakamada and Himemiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:33.57,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Seeing something like that would give you trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.18,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,It's not the time for food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:36.64,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,D-die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:38.56,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Is that really how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.60,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,But right after, she ate two servings of fried chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:43.34,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,There's a delay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:45.60,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,At the time, she was fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:46.79,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,How should I say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:50.28,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,It's like tears suddenly start to flow out of nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.08,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,It's like it suddenly hits you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:55.52,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Just like right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:03:58.80,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.19,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.84,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,Hey, Yakishio, I've got some candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.32,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,Nukumizu, just die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.45,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:08.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,The atmosphere suddenly turned hellish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:11.43,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,We were having so much fun just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:12.70,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:16.72,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,I'm... going for a run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:18.68,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:23.98,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,I'm going to check on the sun bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:30.00,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It seems like they've both gone off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.30,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,I-it's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.62,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,T-take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.90,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:38.19,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,...I kind of feel that way too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I'm not sure why, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:52.80,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It looks like we've come to the Botanical Gardens while walking towards less crowded areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:56.05,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,I-I like botanical gardens, so I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:59.92,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,I feel calm because I can be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:01.96,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,So, was I in the way then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:06.12,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,I'll tolerate you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:08.88,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Komari seems to be in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:09.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:11.68,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,The bench over there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:15.39,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,S-sure, let's take a little break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:15.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.46,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Uh, I'll-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.92,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:19.76,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:20.60,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:21.80,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I'll sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:26.81,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Two wooden chairs placed side by side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:31.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,We sit next to each other, and silently look up at the trees around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:44.56,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,I-It's feels kind of weird, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:45.80,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.84,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,W-We...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:50.24,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,A lot has happened since summer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:52.38,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,W-Well, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:54.77,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,I'm able to talk like this now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.36,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.12,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,When we first met
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:01.64,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,You used to call me 'Nukumizu-kun', didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.31,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:07.20,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,Back then, you were scary and gave off a strange vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:10.49,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,So, are you not scared of me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:14.43,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,Because you're you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:17.58,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:19.04,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:23.83,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,...because you're here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:25.89,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:29.70,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,The seniors, and Yanami and Yakishio too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:32.10,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,We'll stay with Komari from now on, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:34.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I must say, that was a good comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.15,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I thought so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:39.88,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,For some reason, Komari looks exasperated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:41.12,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Eh
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:42.73,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:48.63,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,That's the thing about you, Nukumizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.30,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Everyone says that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.24,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,What do they mean by "that's the thing about you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:52.85,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.54,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,The two of you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:55.40,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Ah, Yakishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Are you done with running?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:58.69,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,I'm all warmed up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:01.58,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,My head's starting to feel pleasantly light and fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.65,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,It's kind of addictive, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.72,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Isn't running bad for your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:06.62,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:07.16,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:09.13,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Everyone's gathered here, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:10.36,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.24,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Yanami-san... you're eating something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:17.41,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,I bought some churros from the stand in front of the amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:20.98,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Here, Lemon-chan and Komari-chan, have a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.55,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Ha! Thanks, Yana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.64,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.84,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It seems that having food in her hands cheered Yanami up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.08,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I felt a bit relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:30.98,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:32.66,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Why are you staring like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:38.15,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Do you want a bite too, Nukumizu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:39.08,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,No, you're already eating it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.28,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,...No, I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:43.32,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,More importantly, the park is about to close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:47.75,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Weren't we here today to take photos for the website?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.82,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Nukumizu-kun, are you not taking any photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.61,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,There's nothing too worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:53.51,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I've already taken some good photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:55.61,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Nukkun, when did you take that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:56.56,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,S-show it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:58.44,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Hey, don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:02.91,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Look, I took a picture of the three of you from behind as you were entering Nonhoi Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:06.27,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It gives off a nice vibe, like we're about to head out on an adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:08.35,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:09.98,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:13.53,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Ah, Nukkun, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.88,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,S-sneak photography!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.88,0:08:16.56,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:19.06,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,No, no, it's not like that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:22.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I can capture everyone's natural expressions like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.52,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,That's why I have to do it without anyone noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:27.48,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Isn't that called sneak photography?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:32.94,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,N-Nukumizu even has a record of secretly taking pictures of me at the city library.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:35.25,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,What? Those photos were taken secretly!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:37.34,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Nukkun, that's not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:39.53,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,If you want to do that, then take pictures of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:43.22,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that okay? Nukumizu-kun does that all the time, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:45.29,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Well, if it's Nukkun, I guess it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:47.28,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Do you want to do it too, Komari-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:50.14,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,Huh? Th-that's way too grown-up a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:53.13,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I don't have a hobby of sneak photography.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:57.23,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Come on, I'm going to take a proper one now, so everyone line up over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.16,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you still being a bit sloppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:00.89,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:03.02,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Put a little more feeling into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.74,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,Get arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:08.34,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Wow, these guys sure have a lot of demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:11.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It's almost closing time, so where should we take the photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:14.27,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Alright, I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:16.62,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Everyone, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:18.76,Anna Yanami,Yanami; Komari; Yakishio,0,0,0,,Oooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:25.72,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:29.98,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,We are in front of Non-chan and Hoi-kun's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:31.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It's right on the way home, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.78,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,If we go away from the station, it'll be a pain to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:37.56,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Nukkun, you're as consistent as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:39.26,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,R-reflect on your actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,No, no, it's not just about being a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.84,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,My phone's battery is about to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.46,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I want to get it over with quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:49.14,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Didn't your phone's battery die the last time we came here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:52.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It seems like my battery drains unusually fast whenever I go out lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.57,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It's still pretty new, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:56.94,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,If you're taking the picture, do it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.18,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:00.40,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Okay, line up the three of you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:02.24,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Don't get in Non-chan and Hoi-kun's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.45,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.88,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Nukkun, aren't you joining in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:05.43,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:07.17,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,There's no point in me joining in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:09.98,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:12.30,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,When we're about to take a group photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:17.32,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Do you really think we're the kind of cold people who would leave you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:19.83,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Yeah, Nukkun, you should join in too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.80,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,Oh, be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:24.53,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Uh, well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:28.78,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,How do you set the self-timer again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:30.87,Anna Yanami,Yanami; Komari; Yakishio,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.60,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Don't rush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:36.10,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Is the timer set like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.63,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Huh, only three seconds left?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:44.45,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Oh, I totally missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.07,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Hey, is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:47.48,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Let me see, let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:49.32,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,Oh, it turned out really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:51.38,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I'm totally not in the shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.89,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I'm cut off in the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:53.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,We need to retake it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:55.78,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:57.33,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,The battery's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:59.98,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that last photo will have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:02.16,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Both of you looked cute in the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.14,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,You looked cute too, Yana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:06.28,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Oh, wait, is that really okay for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:08.10,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Are we really putting that on the website?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:11.38,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,J-just be grateful you're even in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:12.49,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Ehhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:17.26,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,But if I keep complaining, it'll seem like I really want to be in the photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:20.87,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Well, if everyone else is okay with it, then so am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:24.64,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Well, since it's almost time for the train, shall we head back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:25.17,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:28.43,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Wait a moment, I'm going to buy juice from that vending machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:44.33,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,I really do live for this one drink, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:46.98,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,By the way, do you have enough money today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:48.89,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It won't be like last time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:56.30,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Nukumizu-kun, I'm not the same person I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:12:01.22,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,I'm a slightly more grown-up and wise Yanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:05.08,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Saying you're smart makes you sound kind of dumb, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:09.62,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Today, I've already checked the contents of my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:15.50,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,I even accounted for the small change, and with that juice I just bought, I used up all my money perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:16.70,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Not even a single yen left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.68,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,That's right! Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.39,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Even the sales tax was spot on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:21.72,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,That's impressive, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.94,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Can you afford the train fare?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:24.24,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:25.71,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Did you buy a ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:31.45,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,The train fare?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.11,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:34.80,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:37.98,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,I forgot about the train fare back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:39.60,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:41.62,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Should I lend you some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:45.86,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,No, no, I can't borrow any more money from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:47.29,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Komari-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:51.54,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,I only have enough money left for the train ride home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:51.98,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:54.12,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,You don't have to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.42,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,You can pay me back whenever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:56.68,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:58.60,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Lemon-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:00.98,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Yeah, leave it to me, Yana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:02.74,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:05.36,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Having friends really is the best, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:07.78,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.25,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Let's start running then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:09.98,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:13.52,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,I didn't run enough today, so this is really getting me pumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.88,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,No, no, if you could just lend me enough for the train fare.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.91,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,It's fine, we can just run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.47,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Y-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:20.89,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,Nukumizu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:21.44,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.27,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Then Komari and I will take the train—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:25.98,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Since we're all here, why not everyone run?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:27.77,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,It'll be done in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:29.85,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,I-I-I'll take the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.88,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,I'll give you a piggy back if you need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:33.02,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:35.18,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll leave Komari to you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:36.52,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I don't want to get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.31,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,You can't go home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:40.27,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,I'll take care of Komari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:42.74,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Nukkun, give Yana-chan a piggyback if she gets tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:44.03,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,What? She's too heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:45.00,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Nukumizu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:47.52,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,No! That's what I was saying, but not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.59,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,If I need carry someone, it should be Komari.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:51.00,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,D-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:51.69,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.19,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,No, I meant Komari is lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:56.00,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Not that Yanami-san is heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:57.25,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:58.92,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Did you rebound recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.12,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,I haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:04.00,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Every year around this time, I'm in a growth spurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:05.74,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,So, Yana-chan did gain weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:06.84,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Then, let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.17,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:10.89,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,If I start running, my knees make a cracking sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.64,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.73,Lemon Yakishio,Lemon Yakishio,0,0,0,,Nukkun and Komari-chan, you're coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:16.09,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,I'll take the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:19.44,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,This is all your fault, Nukumizu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:21.60,Anna Yanami,Anna Yanami,0,0,0,,I won't let you run away by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:23.68,Chika Komari,Chika Komari,0,0,0,,Don't try to dodge responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.60,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,It's not my fault at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:27.54,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,Kazuhiko Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, don't push my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:30.23,Anna Yanami,Yanami; Komari; Yakishio,0,0,0,,Nukumizu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.96,Anna Yanami,Yanami; Komari; Yakishio,0,0,0,,Take responsibility!
